            <title>[LU-14382] Implement fallocate() support at MDT</title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-14382</link>
                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;fallocate() is supported by ldiskfs, on client and on OST but is missed on MDT for DoM files. The MDT handlers to be updated to include&#160;OST_FALLOCATE PRC handling with subsequent call to underlying backend FS, a MDC should be updated to handle CLIO fallocate request and send RPC, fallocate tests to be extended with DoM layout files&lt;/p&gt;</description>
